text: Aleksandr Akhyun (born 24 June 1892, date of death unknown) was a Russian gymnast. He competed in the men's artistic individual all-around event at the 1912 Summer Olympics. ==References== Category:1892 births Category:Year of death missing Category:Russian male artistic gymnasts Category:Olympic gymnasts of Russia Category:Gymnasts at the 1912 Summer Olympics
